00:54:35.976 --> 00:54:37.351
Victoria.

398
00:54:40.935 --> 00:54:41.893
Beatrice.

399
00:54:42.976 --> 00:54:43.851
Artemis.

400
00:54:44.810 --> 00:54:45.810
Genevive.

401
00:54:46.768 --> 00:54:47.643
Fatima.

402
00:54:48.726 --> 00:54:49.851
Carlotta.

403
00:54:53.393 --> 00:54:54.560
Berapa orang?

404
00:54:59.726 --> 00:55:01.268
